snippet.title: Amber Heard: Johnny Depp ‘threatened to kill me many times’ | 5 News
snippet.description:
► Subscribe to 5 News: http://bit.ly/5NewsSub 

► Johnny Depp's trial against The Sun Newspaper continued today, and it was the turn of his ex-wife Amber Heard to take to the witness box. She claims the actor threatened to kill her many times and accused him of a series of physical and verbal abuse.  

Mr Depp is suing the paper over an article that referred to him as a wife beater - something he denies. 
 
► Johnny Depp libel trial: Amber Heard’s domestic violence “fraudulent”, court hears
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9RPIj49yj6A

The Channel 5 News operation is located in a bespoke state-of-the-art newsroom based at Channel 5, linked to ITN's central technical, editorial and corporate infrastructure.  

ITN changed the TV news landscape when it launched 5 News in 1997, producing Five News for nine years before winning the contract to supply news to Channel 5 again from 2012.
